creator: Snorty Sleep
descriptionHtml:
Gun Sound: Pistol Simulation is the ultimate app that simulates the real-life shooting experience that reproduces the recoils and sounds of all weapons, bombs, and rocket

This app gives people the feeling of holding and shooting a real gun without endangering surrounding people. Unlock gun store collections with all kinds pistol, tazer, bomb, snipers and customized weapon


Playing Mode
1. Weaponry Store Collection
- Pick your favorite gun: Pistol, Desert Egle, Thompson, Sniper, Bomb, Grenade, C4, Rifle, rocket or shotgun, or bazooka,...
- Chose among 4 firing modes: auto, burst, shake, one-shot
- Diversified Combat Environment: Snowy, rainy, and misty

2. Virtual mode
- Open the camera and hold it to shoot in reality
- Go to real-life action with gun changing, smoke throwing and head aiming, etc

Highlights:
🔫 Incredibly smooth, responsive, and simple to utilize the firearm application
🔫 Different strong weapons assortment from various classifications: Gun, machine, rifle, pistol, shotgun,...
🔫 Energizing shot ongoing interaction sound of a firearm
🔫 Awesome UI/UX of the sound of a firearm
🔫 Top notch shot activities like vibration during play sound of a firearm.
🔫 Exciting Impacts and Firearm Sounds.
🔫 Best simulated intelligence utilized for creating to utter the really astonishing sound of weapon.
🔫 Increment your weapon information or utilize the sound of the firearm to trick your companions
